    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS solenoid service and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and a sharp steering rack, ensuring precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior presents with honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and atmospheric induction note remain peak-tier. A visceral driving example focused on kinematic excellence and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
