      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home! It's been a great car for me and is still in really solid shape. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with you today. If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that's ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I'm sure you'll love it!",
      "price": 29800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
