      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock, the mechanical engagement is visceral and direct. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound characteristics. Recent maintenance addressed critical S65 pain points, including rod bearing replacement and refreshed throttle actuators, ensuring optimal valvetrain response. The vehicle exhibits excellent subframe integrity and consistent compression across all cylinders, representing a mechanically sound example of BMW's final high-revving V8.",
